#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/max.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.max"
msgstr "# triton.language.max"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/max.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/max.md:4
msgid "简介：在指定维度上返回其中最大值"
msgstr "Introduction: Returns the maximum value along the specified dimension."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/max.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.max(input, axis=None, return_indices=False, return_indices_tie_break_left=True, keep_dims=False)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/max.md:8
msgid "## 2. OP 规格"
msgstr "## 2. OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/max.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/max.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数名 | 类型 | 说明 |\n"
"| :---: | :---: | --- |\n"
"| `input` | `tensor` | 输入的张量数据 |\n"
"| `axis`   | `int` | 指定在哪个维度上进行规约； axis = none时在所有轴进行规约 |\n"
"| `keep_dims` | `bool` | 保持规约轴规约后的维度 |\n"
"| `return_indices` | `bool` | if true, return index corresponding to the maximum value 除了返回最大值外，返回最大值所在下标 |\n"
"| `return_indices_tie_break_left` | `bool` | 如果多个元素有相同的最大值，返回最左侧最大值的下标  if true, in case of a tie (i.e., multiple elements have the same maximum value), return the left-most index for values that aren’t NaN  |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type | Description |\n"
"| :---: | :---: | --- |\n"
"| `input` | `tensor` | The input tensor data |\n"
"| `axis` | `int` | Specifies which dimension to reduce over; when axis = none, reduce over all axes |\n"
"| `keep_dims` | `bool` | Whether to keep the reduced dimensions after reduction |\n"
"| `return_indices` | `bool` | If true, return the index corresponding to the maximum value; in addition to returning the maximum value, also return the index of the maximum value |\n"
"| `return_indices_tie_break_left` | `bool` | If multiple elements have the same maximum value, return the index of the leftmost maximum value; if true, in case of a tie (i.e., multiple elements have the same maximum value), return the left-most index for values that aren’t NaN |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/max.md:14
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"`tl.tensor`：同`input`的shape的张量\n"
"return_indices = true，返回的index下标类型是fp32类型。\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"`tl.tensor`: A tensor with the same shape as `input`.  \n"
"When `return_indices = true`, the returned index type is `fp32`.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/max.md:16
msgid "参数组合支持："
msgstr "Parameter combination support:"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/max.md:18
msgid ""
"| axis | keep_dims | return_indices | return_indices_tie_break_left  |  规格 |\n"
"| ------ | ------------ | ----------------- | ----------------------------------- | ---|\n"
"|    1 |    TRUE    |      TRUE      |               TRUE                |  支持\n"
"|    1 |    TRUE    |      TRUE      |               FALSE                | 支持\n"
"|    1 |    TRUE    |      FALSE      |               TRUE                | 支持\n"
"|    1 |    TRUE    |      FALSE      |               FALSE                | 支持\n"
"|    1 |   FALSE   |      TRUE      |               TRUE                | 支持\n"
"|    1 |   FALSE   |      TRUE      |               FALSE                | 支持\n"
"|    1 |   FALSE   |      FALSE      |               TRUE                | 支持\n"
"|    1 |   FALSE   |      FALSE      |               FALSE              | 支持\n"
"| None |    TRUE    |      TRUE      |               TRUE               | 不支持\n"
"| None |    TRUE    |      TRUE      |               FALSE              | 不支持\n"
"|  None |    TRUE    |      FALSE      |               TRUE              | 支持\n"
"| None |    TRUE    |      FALSE      |               FALSE              | 支持\n"
"| None |   FALSE   |      TRUE      |               TRUE                | 不支持\n"
"| None |   FALSE   |      TRUE      |               FALSE               | 不支持\n"
"| None |   FALSE   |      FALSE      |               TRUE              | 支持\n"
"| None |   FALSE   |      FALSE      |               FALSE             | 支持\n"
msgstr ""
"| axis | keep_dims | return_indices | return_indices_tie_break_left | Spec |\n"
"|------|-----------|----------------|--------------------------------|------|\n"
"| 1    | TRUE      | TRUE           | TRUE                           | Supported |\n"
"| 1    | TRUE      | TRUE           | FALSE                          | Supported |\n"
"| 1    | TRUE      | FALSE          | TRUE                           | Supported |\n"
"| 1    | TRUE      | FALSE          | FALSE                          | Supported |\n"
"| 1    | FALSE     | TRUE           | TRUE                           | Supported |\n"
"| 1    | FALSE     | TRUE           | FALSE                          | Supported |\n"
"| 1    | FALSE     | FALSE          | TRUE                           | Supported |\n"
"| 1    | FALSE     | FALSE          | FALSE                          | Supported |\n"
"| None | TRUE      | TRUE           | TRUE                           | Not supported |\n"
"| None | TRUE      | TRUE           | FALSE                          | Not supported |\n"
"| None | TRUE      | FALSE          | TRUE                           | Supported |\n"
"| None | TRUE      | FALSE          | FALSE                          | Supported |\n"
"| None | FALSE     | TRUE           | TRUE                           | Not supported |\n"
"| None | FALSE     | TRUE           | FALSE                          | Not supported |\n"
"| None | FALSE     | FALSE          | TRUE                           | Supported |\n"
"| None | FALSE     | FALSE          | FALSE                          | Supported |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/max.md:20
