"|---| ------- | ------ | -------- | ------- | -------- | ------- | -------- | ------- | ------ | ------ | ------ | ----------- |\n"
"|GPU| √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ |\n"
