"|| uint8 | int8 | uint16 | int16 | uint32 | int32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | bf16 | bool/int1 |\n"
"|---| ------- | ------ | -------- | ------- | -------- | ------- | -------- | ------- | ------ | ------ | ------ | ----------- |\n"
"|GPU| √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ |\n"
"|Ascend A2/A3| √ | √ | × | √ | × | √ | × | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/max.md:26
msgid "#### 2.2.2 Shape 支持"
msgstr "#### 2.2.2 Shape Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/max.md:28
msgid ""
"|        | 支持维度范围         |\n"
"| -------- | ---------------------- |\n"
"| GPU    | 无限制 |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3| 无限制 （默认最高8维） |\n"
